name: 2021 The 5th International Conference on Advances in Artificial Intelligence（ICAAI 2021）
content: Publication: Honorable authors are cordially invited to contribute their research papers. All papers submitted to the conference will be subjected to the rigorous peer-review process. For accepted papers, it will be published in the Conference Proceedings, which will be indexed by Ei Compendex, Scopus and other academical databases.
